{"tid":127078,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男友愛賭欠債　女服務生下海陪酒賣淫被逮","createTime":"2017-02-19T23:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T00:13:50.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c09e36bc0936dbf1a08d98a2936e17d6f05ecb30","tid":127078,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T23:30:31.000Z","msg":"張姓女子（25歲）遇上軟爛男，竟為愛下海當酒店小姐，最後為賺更多錢竟加入應召站賣淫。日前張女和廖姓男子在西門町一家旅館進行性交易，遭轄區警方循線逮人。<br />\n<br />\n張女被警方逮捕後，表示自己本來是餐廳服務生，生活相當單純，但一年多前交往一名男友，男友一開始出手闊綽，對她非常好，誰知交往後，張女才發現男友沈迷網路簽賭，在外積欠上百萬元的債務。<br />\n<br />\n債主上門討債，男友只好向張女伸手要錢還債，長久下來兩人入不敷出，張女因為深愛男友，怕他被債主抓到山上斷手斷腳；竟在去年六月下海到中山區酒店陪酒賺錢，不久她認識一名應召站業者，由於張女臉蛋身材姣好，為加速賺錢，張女在應召業者鼓吹下，瞞著男友開始賣淫。<br />\n<br />\n張女化名「小安」，一次性交易價格8千元，沒在酒店上班的日子，就在家等候應召站電話隨時外出賣淫；日前廖姓男子（21歲）在手機通訊軟體，看到應召站發送的廣告圖片，他發現「小安」相片上圍豐滿，立即和應召業者聯繫，約定西門町旅館從事性交易。<br />\n<br />\n張女到旅館後，廖男發現張女胸部與照片有差異，根本沒有那麼「雄偉」，不過廖男雖略感失望，但看到張女仍感到滿意，也因看張女出現被撩起情慾不願再等，因此兩人開始辦事，不料警方早盯上張女，等兩人事畢後，警方現身將他們帶回警局，最後依社會秩序維護法裁處。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/02/19/realtime/3193935.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2Frealtime%2F3193935.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=db53fbd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廖姓男子（左）和張姓女子（右）性交易後遭警方逮捕。圖/記者廖炳棋翻攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/02/19/realtime/3193934.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2Frealtime%2F3193934.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=e6e21705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n應召站發送的「小安」圖片，豐滿上圍騙了不少嫖客上門消費。圖/記者廖炳棋翻攝<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/2/2294289#prettyPhoto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F2%2F2294289%23prettyPhoto&d=YBElpbzmALMQinc%2Bu7edP4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=5c106cef\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/2/2294289#prettyPhoto</a>"},{"pid":"c4c266e3fc9d1489e5b47103e7dbb02889c152d7","tid":127078,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T23:32:06.000Z","msg":"你又話過會養我既！<br />\n<br />\n你唔做舞女搵錢，我點養你呀！"},{"pid":"0d6b0ad283444483f83ede52aae71800a18883b1","tid":127078,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T23:38:24.000Z","msg":"game宣傳咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/c3afodx5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fc3afodx5&h=034425f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6574089fd5e3e30ed01492641da6a736746be96","tid":127078,"uid":83906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T23:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6g814aD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6g814aD.jpg&h=093cc848&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7da4d2ecaf66976b64aad56a3b1e68f3f5cc76f","tid":127078,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T00:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>game宣傳咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/c3afodx5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fc3afodx5&h=034425f2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都諗起依個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}